{"tid":708710,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"日產 GT-R R35 加入警隊　成日本最強警車","createTime":"2018-06-19T13:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T11:11:29.000Z","uid":14600,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"042fd41e2b9175a2e75e287bd243b6d65a2a986d","tid":708710,"uid":14600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:30:54.000Z","msg":"日本栃木縣警署將會使用全國首架日產（Nissan） GT-R R35 警車。據了解，這部警用 GT-R 六成金額為縣民的捐款支付，餘下的則由日產負擔。因為栃木縣是 GT-R 系列的發揚地，而且今年更是這系列的 50 周年紀念，對車廠來說，應是一個不錯的宣傳項目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/35646200_1883807198339313_3489539625238659072_n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F35646200_1883807198339313_3489539625238659072_n.png&h=01179748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當地警方這部新戰車雖然只是一般型號，但配備的 3.8 升 VR38DETT 引擎仍然能提供 570 hp 最大馬力，由靜止加速至 100 km/h 只需 2.7 秒，極速更可達 315 km/h ，將成為日本警隊史上最強的戰車。現行的 GT-R R35 定價約為 239 萬元，日產向警方提供了六折優惠，而餘下的都由市民捐款支付。日後，這部警車將會於北關東自動車道與東北自動車道等地執勤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018-06-19_154336.png \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018-06-19_154336.png%20&h=f8fd483b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018-06-19_154424.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018-06-19_154424.png&h=614d770c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，日本警方亦曾使用不少跑車作警車之用。埼玉縣警察就採用了 Supra 及 GT-R R34 作警車，而神奈川縣警察亦曾使用過日產的 S30Z 、 Z32 、 R32/R33 GT-R 等車型。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018-06-19_154459.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018-06-19_154459.png&h=9e290f14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018-06-19_154519.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018-06-19_154519.png&h=2c073526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018-06-19_154304.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018-06-19_154304.png&h=ad6744f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018-06-19_154351.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018-06-19_154351.png&h=af100fd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018-06-19_154409.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018-06-19_154409.png&h=d4be4a5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://unews.io/s/K7x9e8YUK9w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funews.io%2Fs%2FK7x9e8YUK9w&d=ZgTJDYtF54CW5Yu6zMH7zhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=9f5edc26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unews.io/s/K7x9e8YUK9w</a>"},{"pid":"c3e0e5933f1209b00eecd8f3d501a77a007d2bab","tid":708710,"uid":171829,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DdXq6fAUwAESO2J.jpg:small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDdXq6fAUwAESO2J.jpg%3Asmall&h=d91530fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DdXrCSPVMAAfRzo.jpg:small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDdXrCSPVMAAfRzo.jpg%3Asmall&h=36c07d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DdXrDVhU8AEdSyJ.jpg:small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fme